    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cloth coverings of various materials cut to cover a horse's body from around the withers to the rump and, in front, around the chest; used to protect a horse or discourage growth of a heavy coat.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
